---
layout: base.njk
title: Ghoul2 Browser Tools
---
  <header>
    <h1>Ghoul2 Browser Tools</h1>
    <p>Browser-based tools for working with Jedi Knight 2/3's Ghoul2 (<code>.glm</code>/<code>.gla</code>) model &amp; skeletal animation formats. Runs entirely in your browser — no upload, no server.</p>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="tool-grid">
      {% for tool in tools %}
      <a class="tool-card" href="{{ tool.href }}">
        <h2>{{ tool.title }}</h2>
        <p>{{ tool.description }}</p>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </main>
